    "subType": "mutation",
    "description": "<p>As a Main Action, emit a wave of psychic terror in a 10-meter radius. Your allies can resist it, but all other living creatures must make a Morale check. A creature may choose to continue fighting even if it fails the check, but it then takes 1d6 damage per 2 character levels you possess, rounded up. If reduced to zero hit points this way, it regains one HP and flees. You may trigger this wave only once per scene. If used out of combat, this power grants a +2 bonus to any social skill checks reliant on intimidation.</p>",
